instruction: Create a rap verse about algorithms.
output:
Verse 1: 
Algorithms, they're the ones that help us get along, 
Synthesize, analyze, structure and sort right and wrong. 
A bit of help from a machine, according to these instructions, 
Sit back and watch it work, not a lot of contradiction. 

Verse 2: 
Adapting to all cases, quickly computing the data, 
It can do your math and science, makes life a whole lot easier, yeah. 
From machine learning to deep learning, takes away the hassle, 
Everything you want and need, no more big or small. 

Chorus: 
Algorithms do it all, algorithms do it all, 
From analysis to heuristics, all solved in a much smoother haul. 
Algorithms do it all, algorithms do it all, 
A productive way to reach a conclusion without fail.
